headline: Why Centene (CNC) Stock Is Trading Lower Today
summary: Shares of health coverage company Centene (NYSE:CNC) fell 3% in the morning session after investor concerns continued to weigh on the stock following a significant financial challenge disclosed by the company's CEO last week.
